<!--
  Refinery — CLEANED feed list (draft for Sift import), 2026-07-01.
  Based on subscriptions.opml + taste-based cuts. Original left intact.

  CUTS applied:
   - News: Yahoo News + Fox News (Latest)  → source of the sports/celebrity noise
   - Finance: Seeking Alpha, Motley Fool, CNBC Mad Money (opinion/pick spam, contradictory
              buy/sell on the same stock); Yahoo Finance + Fox Business (high-volume overlap)
   - YouTube folder (22 channels)           → videos, not reading; belong in YouTube, not Refinery
  ADDS: Import AI, Latent Space (AI analysis, to match Nate/Stratechery taste)
  PENDING (not yet applied here):
   - [XX] folder renaming (backlog X1 — needs Tom's number assignments)
   - Reddit: kept for now, but flaky (backlog R1 — decide integrate vs drop)
   - Top-10 stocks: add per-ticker feeds here once Tom gives the 10 tickers (backlog F1)
